        Constructor for Crime
        Parameters:
        date - the date the crime was committed in seconds
        address - the approximate address of the crime committed
        type - the type of crime committed (assault, murder, rape, etc.)
        latitude - the latitude of the location where the crime was committed
        longitude - the longitude of the location where the crime was committed
        linkid - the linkId of the location where the crime was committed
